Hello,


I wanted to raise awareness that the wiki link
<https://webarchive.jira.com/wiki/display/Heritrix> present in the Github
README <https://github.com/InternetArchive/heritrix3#3-getting-started> is
now asking for authentication into Atlassian Cloud. I suspect this is not
what is supposed to happen, and I wanted to raise awareness so we can
hopefully get it back online, since that is the only URL for documentation
(that I know of).


  Thanks for your help,
  -- /v\atthew
